author: lu ate
content:
Absolutely love this place! Even though it can get super busy, I like that it still feels like a local secret and unless you go searching for it, youâ€™ll hardly ever just stumble upon it!
The vegan/vegetarian cabbage dish and the chicken tikka masala are must haves when available, very delicious!
All vego curries are also vegan and to my knowledge, ALL curries are gluten free!
